text: Trudering-Riem (Central Bavarian: Trudaring-Ream) is a borough in Munich, Bavaria. The districts of Trudering and Riem merged to form Trudering-Riem. == Other websites == * www.muenchen.de - Trudering * www.muenchen.de - Riem * History * Abendzeitung Category:Boroughs of Munich
